{"tid":937087,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"教你地賭馬必輸既方法","createTime":"2018-12-11T09:24:56.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-11T11:14:25.000Z","uid":123335,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3f56c7dab21caf5545c352fc509e708d0a879052","tid":937087,"uid":123335,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T09:24:56.000Z","msg":"賭馬逢賭必輸<br />\n呢方面我諗冇人比我更熟<br />\n<br />\n我必輸唔係靠買大冷門咁低莊<br />\n而係買熱門，次熱門都逢賭必輸<br />\n當中有冇秘訣？<br />\n絕對係有既。<br />\n<br />\n第一，過份妄想細微既數據會預示賽果<br />\nEg 用過往同程紀錄既時間作為重要既比較指標，例如A馬上場跑1650m時間係1:42:05；B馬上場跑1:42:58，所以呢場重注買A馬，結果B馬贏 。<br />\n<br />\n原因好簡單：<br />\n<em><strong>過往戰績並不代表將來表現。</strong></em><br />\n<br />\n用micro 既目光去賭馬<br />\n一定會輸到你仆街"},{"pid":"5015fab89ad3d13f969e84ec3167a8f06bee33d3","tid":937087,"uid":33730,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T09:28:12.000Z","msg":"跟住你買乜咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ef6c09f188cc05c72e2a39693252ff7d10f68eed","tid":937087,"uid":332,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T09:30:23.000Z","msg":"聽日你仲唔贏硬，比你留意到下次點買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1257bf68b31d6cc7dff96cfce952066e490c0636","tid":937087,"uid":43861,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T09:30:28.000Z","msg":"有彪哥冇窮人"},{"pid":"2bf96681c6fb2cd35eb779730a128c3437ad3e9a","tid":937087,"uid":123335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5015fab89ad3d13f969e84ec3167a8f06bee33d3","tid":937087,"uid":33730,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T09:28:12.000Z","msg":"跟住你買乜咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-11T09:30:53.000Z","msg":"我買馬個策略係用micro-data analysis 既目光去買<br />\n每注飛個背後都可以寫篇1000字論文去解釋背後理念<br />\n非常之make sense <br />\n但結果就異常地輸到仆街"},{"pid":"36ed5479deceb87f5e656ce8157748d2987ceb7a","tid":937087,"uid":224672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":